(145, 'greenpark2_sidebar_about_content', '  <ul>\r\n  	<li>\r\n  		 <a href="http://gnome.org">GNOME</a>.Asia was organized by the GNOME.Asia Committee and Quang Trung Software City in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. <a href="index.html?page_id=70">More info >></a>		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li id="text-9" class="widget widget_text">			<div class="textwidget">Please visit the <strong><a href="http://live.gnome.org/GnomeAsia/2009">GNOME.Asia Wiki</a></strong> for more info about talks, projects and participants at the event.</div>\r\n		</li></ul>\r\n\r\n<ul class="group">\r\n<li id="text-10" class="widget widget_text">			<div class="textwidget"><!-- Start of Flickr Badge -->\r\n<style type="text/css">\r\n#flickr_badge_source_txt {padding:0; font: 11px Arial, Helvetica, Sans serif; color:#666666;}\r\n#flickr_badge_icon {display:block !important; margin:0 !important; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;}\r\n#flickr_icon_td {padding:0 5px 0 0 !important;}\r\n.flickr_badge_image {text-align:center !important;}\r\n.flickr_badge_image img {border: 1px solid black !important;}\r\n#flickr_www {display:block; padding:0 10px 0 10px !important; font: 11px Arial, Helvetica, Sans serif !important; color:#3993ff !important;}\r\n#flickr_badge_uber_wrapper a:hover,\r\n#flickr_badge_uber_wrapper a:link,\r\n#flickr_badge_uber_wrapper a:active,\r\n#flickr_badge_uber_wrapper a:visited {text-decoration:none !important; background:inherit !important;color:#3993ff;}\r\n#flickr_badge_wrapper {}\r\n#flickr_badge_source {padding:0 !important; font: 11px Arial, Helvetica, Sans serif !important; color:#666666 !important;}\r\n</style>\r\n<table id="flickr_badge_uber_wrapper" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" border="0"><tr><td><a href="http://www.flickr.com" id="flickr_www">www.<strong style="color:#3993ff">flick<span style="color:#ff1c92">r</span></strong>.com</a><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" border="0" id="flickr_badge_wrapper">\r\n<script type="text/javascript" src="http://www.flickr.com/badge_code_v2.gne?count=10&display=latest&size=t&layout=v&source=all_tag&tag=gnomeasia09"></script>\r\n</table>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<!-- End of Flickr Badge -->\r\n</div>\r\n		</li><li id="rss-8" class="widget widget_rss"><div class="sb-title widgettitle"><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/rss/tag/gnomeasia'' title=''Syndicate this content''><img style=''background:orange;color:white;border:none;'' width=''14'' height=''14'' src=''wp-includes/images/rss.png'' alt=''RSS'' /></a> <a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/'' title=''SlideShare feed for Slideshows for Tag: gnomeasia''>Latest GNOME.Asia Slides</a></div><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/nckuhuahua2/game-update'' title='' Abstract:  生活不忘娛樂，來點輕鬆的小遊戲增添一些歡樂吧!使用 Andes Core™ N1213的platform SoC 所建構的發展系統硬體主板，並搭配 3.5 吋 320×240 畫質Panel，展示了此平台開發掌上型遊戲機，遊戲軟體與 Andes Core 的完美結合。 趁著這次 COSCUP / GNOME.Asia 的機會跟大家分享一些在 Embedded Linux 上執行 Emulator 的使用心得。    Bio:  交通大學電子工程系學生，對嵌入式系統領域稍有涉獵。Thomas 之前於晶心科技，一間台灣 32 位元處理器的 IC 設計公司打工。在台灣心的開發平台，都靠 Game Emulator 騙吃騙喝。近年來由於工作與興趣關係研究 Game Emulator，熱於探索應用 […]''>Have Fun on Andes Platform -- Game Emulator an Overview</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/jouston/coscup2010-opening-0815'' title='' COSCUP / GNOME.Asia 第二天開幕式 […]''>Coscup2010 opening 0815</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/jouston/coscup2010-0814-opening'' title='' COSCUP / GNOME.Asia 2010開幕式 […]''>Coscup2010 0814 opening</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.slideshare.net/yurenju/javascript-in-linux-desktop'' title='' […]''>Javascript in Linux Desktop</a></li></ul></li><li id="rss-4" class="widget widget_rss"><div class="sb-title widgettitle"><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://blogsearch.google.com/blogsearch_feeds?hl=en&q=fossasia&scoring=d&ie=utf-8&num=10&output=rss'' title=''Syndicate this content''><img style=''background:orange;color:white;border:none;'' width=''14'' height=''14'' src=''wp-includes/images/rss.png'' alt=''RSS'' /></a> <a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&q=fossasia&ie=utf-8&tbm=blg&tbs=sbd:1'' title=''Results 1 - 10 of about 638 for fossasia.''>Blogs</a></div><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://describewebde.com/hdtv-space-forum.de'' title=''Fossasia.org. FOSSASIA. Securedloantips.org. Secured Loan Tips. Novolineonline.net. Novoline Online. Porquelodigoyo.com. porquelodigoyo.com. Katz.cd. DownloadWeb - download Movies, TV Shows, Games, Software and more! Latest Additions ... […]''>Hdtv-space-forum.de - Hdtv-space-forum, HDTV, LCD-TV, 3D, OLED, LED</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://describewebit.com/stylishtemplate.com'' title=''FOSSASIA. Solmelia.com. Sol Melia - Sol Melia mobile. Bloganalisis.com. Blog Análisis - Haz un ... de Tu Sitio y Gana Visitas. Lufthansa-usa.com. Lufthansa - Online flight offers | No booking fee | Sale fares to Europe. Latest Additions ... […]''>Stylishtemplate.com - Stylishtemplate, website templates, web ...</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://describewebit.com/vivovenezia.com'' title=''FOSSASIA. Fanslave.de. Fans, Facebook, Fanslave, Marketing, Fan, Guenstigen. 11rate.com. 11 PLAYERS RATE. Dennisyang.com. dennis yang dot com. Clean-stone.ru. Природный камень. Продажа природного натурального и искусственного камня. ... […]''>Vivovenezia.com - Vivovenezia, vivovenezia.com</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://newsofware.blogspot.com/2011/06/pdf-spam-con-redireccionamiento-en.html'' title=''... hxxp: / / nspcommunity.net/wiki/images/e/e8/Small-loan-business.pdf; hxxp: / / wiki.fossasia.org/images/6/67/Ship-loans.pdf; hxxp: / vuas.net / / ~ dpmccann / mw / images / real-estate-hipotecas loans.pdf. Follow @gansomer ... […]''>freesotfware: PDF spam con redireccionamiento en sitios .edu</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://nguyentieuhau.wordpress.com/2011/06/01/huong-dan-cai-dat-linux-mint-11-tren-may-da-co-windows-7/'' title=''7z abiword apache aqualung audio biến đổi khí hậu chiến tranh cài đặt hệ điều hành cài đặt ứng dụng mới Debian dvd dòng lệnh ebook fedora firefox flash font fossasia 2010 grub2 ibus iso lamp Linux linux mint lubuntu lxde mysql môi ... […]''>Hướng dẫn cài đặt Linux Mint 11 trên máy đã có Windows 7 ...</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://preetam.net/using-google-docs-to-share-news-clippings-wit'' title=''... communities (1); culture (1); design (1); educamp (1); educampsg2 (1); fed5b (1); food (1); fossasia (1); fujixerox (1); hardware (1); hongkong (1); insurance (1); internet (1); internetcafe (1); ipad (1); iphone (1); ishootfilm (1) ... […]''>Using Google Docs to share news clippings with your learners ...</a></li></ul></li><li id="rss-6" class="widget widget_rss"><div class="sb-title widgettitle"><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://identi.ca/api/statuses/user_timeline/gnomeasia.atom'' title=''Syndicate this content''><img style=''background:orange;color:white;border:none;'' width=''14'' height=''14'' src=''wp-includes/images/rss.png'' alt=''RSS'' /></a> <a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/gnomeasia'' title=''Updates from gnomeasia on Identi.ca!''>GNOME.Asia Twitter</a></div><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/15484865'' title=''The numbers are real - still unbelievable - 1400 participants at GNOME.Asia 2009 in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. […]''>The numbers are real - still unbelievable - 1400 participants at GNOME.Asia 2009 in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/14248247'' title=''First version of GNOME.Asia Schedule is online at http://2009.gnome.asia/?page_id=3 […]''>First version of GNOME.Asia Schedule is online at http://2009.gnome.asia/?page_id=3</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/14120364'' title=''A Map Party is being organized at the summit, where participants can learn to collect GEO data with GPS devices and create a map. […]''>A Map Party is being organized at the summit, where participants can learn to collect GEO data with GPS devices and create a map.</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/13995484'' title=''Greetings to organizers of #AsiaSource3. We hope to see you at GNOME.Asia. Please check out http://gnome.asia […]''>Greetings to organizers of #AsiaSource3. We hope to see you at GNOME.Asia. Please check out http://gnome.asia</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/13992642'' title=''80 volunteers are ready to welcome you at GNOME.Asia 2009 in Ho Chi Minh City in Vietnam from Nov. 20-22. Please join us […]''>80 volunteers are ready to welcome you at GNOME.Asia 2009 in Ho Chi Minh City in Vietnam from Nov. 20-22. Please join us</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://identi.ca/notice/11949713'' title=''GNOME.Asia Meet up for Organization Thu, Oct, 15, 7pm, - St Trung Nguyen Cafe, 7 Nguyen Van Chiem, Saigon: http://bit.ly/895WI […]''>GNOME.Asia Meet up for Organization Thu, Oct, 15, 7pm, - St Trung Nguyen Cafe, 7 Nguyen Van Chiem, Saigon: http://bit.ly/895WI</a></li></ul></li><li id="rss-7" class="widget widget_rss"><div class="sb-title widgettitle"><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://news.google.com.vn/news?pz=1&cf=all&ned=vi_vn&hl=vi&q=fossasia&cf=all&output=rss'' title=''Syndicate this content''><img style=''background:orange;color:white;border:none;'' width=''14'' height=''14'' src=''wp-includes/images/rss.png'' alt=''RSS'' /></a> <a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://news.google.com.vn/news?pz=1&ned=vi_vn&hl=vi&q=fossasia'' title=''Google Tin tức''>Tiếng Việt News</a></div><ul><li>An error has occurred; the feed is probably down. Try again later.</li></ul></li><li id="rss-5" class="widget widget_rss"><div class="sb-title widgettitle"><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://news.google.com/news?pz=1&cf=all&ned=us&hl=en&q=fossasia&cf=all&output=rss'' title=''Syndicate this content''><img style=''background:orange;color:white;border:none;'' width=''14'' height=''14'' src=''wp-includes/images/rss.png'' alt=''RSS'' /></a> <a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://news.google.com/news?pz=1&ned=us&hl=en&q=fossasia'' title=''Google News''>In the news</a></div><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&fd=R&usg=AFQjCNGUAmrs0Q0WPDjEE04YdA8VwKOWiQ&url=http://www.casertanews.it/public/articoli/2011/05/17/art_20110517075944.htm'' title=''La settima edizione della due giorni ecologica all''insegna del riciclaggioCaserta NewsL''edizione di quest''anno rappresenta la naturale conclusione di un percorso formativo che ha visto coinvolti quali parti attive sia il Comune di Santa Maria La Fossa, sia i rappresentanti di classe e sia il locale nucleo di Protezione civile. ...and more » […]''>La settima edizione della due giorni ecologica all''insegna del riciclaggio - Caserta News</a></li></ul></li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class="group">\r\n<li id="text-7" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Co-Organizer</div>			<div class="textwidget">ICT Ho Chi Minh City Government<a href="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/ict-ho-chi-minh-city1.png"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/ict-ho-chi-minh-city1.png" alt="ICT Ho Chi Minh City, ICT-HCM - SỞ THÔNG TIN VÀ TRUYỀN THÔNG TP. HỒ CHÍ MINH" title="ICT Ho Chi Minh City, ICT-HCM - SỞ THÔNG TIN VÀ TRUYỀN THÔNG TP. HỒ CHÍ MINH" width="135" height="69" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-279" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\nQuang Trung Software City<a href="http://www.mbm.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/gtsc-logo1.png" alt="gtsc-logo" title="gtsc-logo" width="115" height="92" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-250" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-3" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Silver Sponsor</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://sun.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-48" title="SUN Microsystems" src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/sun_logo.png" alt="SUN Microsystems" width="145" height="63" /></a></div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-6" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Bronze Sponsor</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/vn/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-45" title="IBM" src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/ibm.png" alt="IBM" width="135" height="45" /></a></div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-5" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Other Sponsors</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://google.com"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/google_logo.png" alt="google_logo" title="google_logo" width="135" height="68" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-46" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://fossasia.com"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/fossasia-logo.png" alt="fossasia" title="fossasia" width="135" height="63" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-321" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://www.intel.com/jobs/Vietnam/"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/intel-logo1.png" alt="intel-logo" title="intel-logo" width="110" height="72" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-245" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://www.lemote.com"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/lemote_logo.gif" alt="lemote" title="lemote" width="135" height="41" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-353" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://ghp-fareast.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/ghp-fareast.jpg" alt="ghp-fareast" width="135" height="117" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://www.asianux.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/Asianux.png" alt="Asianux Vietnam" title="Asianux Vietnam" width="135" height="48" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241" /></a></div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-2" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Media Partner</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://www.pcworld.com.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/pcworld_the_gioi_vi_tinh_vietnam.gif" alt="The Gioi Vi Tinh, PCWorld Vietnam" title="The Gioi Vi Tinh, PCWorld Vietnam" width="135" height="33" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-297" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://baodatviet.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/baodatviet.png" alt="Bao Dat Viet" title="Bao Dat Viet" width="135" height="42" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-239" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://www.imark.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/imark.png" alt="imark" title="imark" width="110" height="41" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://baodautu.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/baodautu-vn.jpg" alt="baodautu-vn" title="baodautu-vn" width="135" height="35" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-342" /></a></div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-8" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Education Partner</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://www.hcmup.edu.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/Dai_Hoc_Su_Pham_University_of_Pedagogy_Ho_Chi_Min_logo.png" alt="Dai Hoc Su Pham - University of Pedagogy Ho Chi Min" title="Dai Hoc Su Pham - University of Pedagogy Ho Chi Min" width="135" height="79" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-334" /></a>University of Pedagogy\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://www.saigontech.edu.vn"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/saigontech_logo.gif" alt="Saigontech" title="Saigontech" width="122" height="78" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318" /></a></div>\r\n		</li><li id="text-4" class="widget widget_text"><div class="sb-title widgettitle">Community Partner</div>			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://lxde.org"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/lxde-logo.png" alt="LXDE and Lightweight Linux" title="lxde-logo" width="135" height="79" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-53" /></a>\r\n<br/>\r\n<a href="http://opensolaris.org"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2009/10/opensolaris.png" alt="opensolaris" title="opensolaris" width="135" height="155" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-323" /